# ClawCommand Project

OpenClaw Control Dashboard — file-scanner first, optional runtime control.

## Context

- **Phase 1:** Read-only scanner (`openclaw-scan`), snapshot upload, dashboard with inventory, validation, policy, patches
- **Phase 2:** Optional Node Agent daemon for live orchestration
- **Monorepo:** `packages/scanner`, `packages/api`, `packages/dashboard`

## Key Conventions

- Scanner is read-only: no shell execution, no remote control, no secret extraction
- Every issue links to evidence (file + line) and recommended fix
- Always show "Based on scan at <timestamp>"
- Distinguish static state (scanner) vs live state (daemon)

